data.description: Welcome to 727 Arrow Street! This beautiful Craftsman-style home is nestled in Tyndall Parkway on 1.12 Acres, just 6 miles from Tyndall Airforce Base. With a touch of Florida Cottage Vibes, this home has all of the old home charm with modern conveniences. With 9.5-foot ceilings, engineered hardwood throughout the living area, a newly remodeled guest bath and an open-concept kitchen with granite countertops, this home is your canvas. It does need a little TLC but with minor things being done to bring it to completion, It cold be incredible!There are 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this house also includes a spacious bonus room that could be used as a living space, office, or gym. The kitchen includes custom cabinetry including pot drawers and rolling shelving in the pantry. The spacious attic makes for great storage along with the spacious laundry/utility room.You'll find that this home sits on over an Acre of fenced-in land which includes a custom walk-in chicken coop, a 24 x 32 workshop, a 32 ft. above ground pool, and a 20 x 27 deck to enjoy grilling by the pool and entertaining guests.This property is large, open, and perfect for you!
